items.title: UW MEM-C Debuts Online
items.excerpt: UW MEM-C makes its online debut! Please check out our new and developing site. You can learn more about our research programs and team.

items.title: UW to host $15.6M NSF-funded center for innovation, education in materials science
items.excerpt: UW MEM-C was recently featured in a UW News article detailing how this center became the second of its kind on the West coast.
